<template>
  <v-card
    :elevation="12"
    style="width: 600px"
    v-for="item in contacts"
    :key="item.job_id"
  >
    <v-icon style="width=50;" icon="mdi-account-circle" />
    <v-card-title>{{ item.u_name }}</v-card-title>
  </v-card>
</template>
<script setup>
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { computed, onMounted } from "vue";
const store = useStore();
const contacts = computed(() => {
  return store.state.contractor.contacts;
});
onMounted(() => {
  store.dispatch("triggerSetContacts");
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
